,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T05:43:58.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">值得做 應該做 日日做<br />\n<br />\n值得遮 應該遮 日日遮<br />\n<br />\n值得塞 應該塞 日日塞<br />\n<br />\n值得叫 應該叫 日日叫<br />\n<br />\n值得屌 應該屌 日日屌<br />\n<br />\n值得打 應該打 日日打<br />\n<br />\n值得買 應該買 日日買<br />\n<br />\n值得行 應該行 日日行<br />\n<br />\n值得帶 應該帶 日日帶<br />\n<br />\n值得戴 應該戴 日日戴<br />\n<br />\n值得幫 應該幫 日日幫<br />\n<br />\n值得封 應該封 日日封<br />\n<br />\n</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"14b9d23a8b1bb664ddbe8ab4ff659ce645e423c8","tid":1740843,"uid":312332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T05:44:02.000Z","msg":"連儂牆：絕對係 50歲以上人士既資訊來源<br />\n<br />\n無連儂牆後果<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無左連儂牆，佢地只會返去睇CCTVB</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">1：連儂牆位置分主區及副區</span></span><br />\n主區： 圖片要美化，排列要工整<br />\n副區：屬於隨時陣亡/被清洗區，唔洗太靚<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2：連儂牆急需擴展<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><em>建議找尋真黃店，借佢半邊外牆興建連儂牆，記得要美圖，仲要好聲好氣問，可以拒絕</em></span><br />\n~借用位置不得高於一半，否則影響店舖透光<br />\n~借用大細可長可短，壁報板大細都可以<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">變相成為驗證真真真黃店!!!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">做人要有禮貌，拒絕唔代表對方藍</span></span></em></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">3：最重要係內容</span></span><br />\n<br />\n請大家更改連儂牆內容<br />\n<br />\n警暴是果，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">貪腐政權是因</span><br />\n<br />\n我發現大家由6月反修例開始，比政府spin到去黑社會，再由黑社會spin到去警暴<br />\n<br />\n但係最終源頭，都係政權貪腐，勾結黑幫，包庇警暴，係 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">官鄉警黑勾結</span></span><br />\n<br />\n連儂牆一定要 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Post大量政權貪污資訊</span></span><br />\n<br />\n4：香港人一定要打岩政治旗號<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">反貪污</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">反黑社會</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">反警暴</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">打黑反貪，反官鄉警黑勾結</span></span>"},{"pid":"a0d15c00bd6cf9b460af5bd9159da814365da514","tid":1740843,"uid":1884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T05:44:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e701e331cd571464875ae43260df4a0aa242c04c","tid":1740843,"uid":20288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T05:45:49.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"75545bef6fc5df7cb52404b2a8b6c30bbc7ca6bf","tid":1740843,"uid":1884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T05:45:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"103f09be6b2d1a5b4add37dcb30e8fc004ece224","tid":1740843,"uid":65353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T05:45:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a17579470ffab155a555a2aff5de2cd73e6bf582","tid":1740843,"uid":65353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T05:46:46.000Z","msg":"推阿"},{"pid":"da0f6ce88265cc3a2fe823307ac30e52781895ea","tid":1740843,"uid":41159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T05:47:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43b2736e955a20907316f9b03ffc48482dee3d74","tid":1740843,"uid":58797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T05:49:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b009a710b9f23fde82d1d19216194be92d659dfb","tid":1740843,"uid":1884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T05:50:02.000Z","msg":"幫手推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"949f6d06c299ea7914b38ef321d9a1aff401366a","tid":1740843,"uid":36014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T05:51:37.000Z","msg":"630既時間係最好<br />\n之前真係起唔到身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosa